3948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-09T20:01:59.000Z","msg":"101 幾切合現實，樣衰的好男人"},{"pid":"5fbeab55ebbd276ad98d417e9ddab9c23feb1711","tid":55954,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-10T04:40:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>共通點：<br />\n<br />\n兩套都係1991年係日本首播同埋都有江口洋介演出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正評：東京愛情故事<br />\n負皮：101次求婚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n101次求婚既淺野溫子我覺得演技有D浮誇, 相比之下鈴木保奈美好少少<br />\n不過兩套劇既男角都好正"},{"pid":"ba036b7b875aadfe72ad14662a064f6c99c1c56f","tid":55954,"uid":70415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-10T05:25:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>101 幾切合現實，樣衰的好男人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得東愛織田裕二都唔係話好靚仔，個樣幾鄉下仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"165791475f43d14b11136d732e5eeb2cdf7ad0f8","tid":55954,"uid":7363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-10T12:52:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>101 幾切合現實，樣衰的好男人</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我覺得東愛織田裕二都唔係話好靚仔，個樣幾鄉下仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為講佢由鄉下地方愛媛黎到東京做野，所以角色上要搵個樣土土地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8a38ea252183a2cb9977990f0f5442da2e2df79","tid":55954,"uid":7363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-10T12:54:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>東愛無得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最鍾意呢d唔係大團圓結局既愛情片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認同，唔完美嘅結局更令人懷念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb8a62192efa695a396f659a46916a1cf17d46a","tid":55954,"uid":70415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-10T13:21:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>東愛無得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最鍾意呢d唔係大團圓結局既愛情片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認同，唔完美嘅結局更令人懷念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我覺得東愛幾反映到現實社會愛情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多人最後一齊個一半都唔係自己最鍾意個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n明明大家都鍾意對方，但係就係無可能長遠走落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}